Bahrain Telecom Faces ‘Technical’ Problems With Internet

-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 
2011-02-16T09:26:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/bahrain-telecom-faces-technical-problems-with-internet.html
Bahrain Telecommunications Co., the
nation’s largest phone company, is experiencing "technical
difficulties" with internet services, Chief Executive Officer
Peter Kaliaropoulos said today. The company is "investigating"
the disruptions, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
